# Files excluded from upload to Vercel.
#
# Anything listed here is invisible to Vercel's build/deploy pipeline,
# so it can never be auto-detected as a Serverless Function or bloat
# the deployment artefact.
#
# IMPORTANT: this file is shared between every Vercel project linked
# to the repo (matlens-storybook AND the main app). Only put things
# here that NEITHER project needs at deploy time.

# Test sources never run in production — keep them out of the
# Function count and out of the bundle. Without this rule, Vercel
# auto-detects every `api/**/*.test.js` as a Serverless Function and
# the Hobby plan tops out at 12.
**/*.test.js
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# Local-only artefacts that no project needs at build time.
coverage/
.vitest-cache/
.claude/
.serena/
.vscode/
